			Once you turn in the shadowed scythe, You will receive a note (only a reminder he owes you), and instructions on what else to obtain.<BR>
<BR>
The items are:<BR>
Fungus Eye  - Mortuary Fungus in Unrest<BR>
Shadowed Knife - Island Goblin Headmaster in OOT<BR>
Fire Opal<BR>
<BR>
Give those items to him and the note, and the harvester should be yours....
